OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FSteak, coffee and cheese   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftagged as shoplifting rises
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Steaks and cheese are being fitted with
OL,6, security tags and coffee replaced with 
OL,7, dummy jars, as supermarkets battle to  
OL,8, curb a rise in shoplifting.            
OL,10,FSome stores are also limiting the      
OL,11,Fnumber of items on shelves in an       
OL,12,Fattempt to reduce theft.               
OL,14,FIt comes as data analysed by the BBC   
OL,15,Fshowed shoplifting offences had now    
OL,16,Freturned to pre-pandemic levels as the 
OL,17,Fcost of living rises.                  
OL,19,FRetailers say they are spending heavily
OL,20,Fon anti-crime measures.                
